  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态图，描述HealthTech_PatientRecords这个核心系统是怎么被开发、部署和运行的。核心角色是Developer，他既要管基础设施，也要管Kubernetes配置。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "Kubernetes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Developer是中心节点。那CommonConfig呢？它跟Infrastructure和Kubernetes是什么关系？是双向的还是单向依赖？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Developer",
        "CommonConfig",
        "Infrastructure",
        "Kubernetes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "CommonConfig是共享配置层，Infrastructure和Kubernetes都要依赖它。而且Kubernetes和CommonConfig之间其实是互相影响的——配置改了可能要重启集群，集群升级也会回写配置。所以画双向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CommonConfig",
        "Infrastructure",
        "Kubernetes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把CommonConfig放在中间层，上面连Infrastructure和Kubernetes，都是双向。Developer也直接连CommonConfig，这样他能修改配置。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CommonConfig",
        "Infrastructure",
        "Kubernetes",
        "Developer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，然后Application要基于CommonConfig运行，最终服务于HealthTech_PatientRecords。Application和HealthTech_PatientRecords之间是单向的，应用支撑患者记录系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Application",
        "CommonConfig",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：CommonConfig到Application是单向，Application到HealthTech_PatientRecords也是单向。HealthTech_PatientRecords在最顶层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CommonConfig",
        "Application",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，HealthTech_PatientRecords是最终业务系统，放在最上面或者最下面都可以，但它是起点也是终点——Developer从需求出发，最终交付到这个系统。所以HealthTech_PatientRecords和Developer之间也要有连线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "Developer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。整个图从HealthTech_PatientRecords出发，经过Developer向下延伸到Infrastructure和Kubernetes，中间CommonConfig作为配置中枢，最后Application回连到患者记录系统形成闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "Kubernetes",
        "CommonConfig",
        "Application"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
